<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[بَزَمَ]</span> الناقة: فَطَرَها <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>و <span class="c4">[بَزَا]</span> البازي بَزْواً: إِذا تطاول.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">والبَزَوَان:</span> الوثب.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>... فعَل، بفتح العين، يفعِل، بكسرها<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
